data.description: Nestled in a prime location, this two-story townhome offers comfort and unparalleled convenience. Easy access to everyday necessities, shopping and commuter highways - making life a breeze. Find lot of natural light throughout, open flowing living areas, wood-floors on the main level, an appealing updated kitchen, and a walkout deck which provides a welcoming space for relaxation and entertainment. Downstairs, it's a big open space that includes a walkout which opens to a private patio with desirable views, offering a nice escape. With two bedrooms, two baths, and an attached two-stall garage, this townhome combines modern amenities with a coveted location, making it an ideal choice for homeowners. Tour today!
